  affinity:

      preferredDuringSchedulingIgnoredDuringExecution:
        - weight: 100
          podAffinityTerm:
            labelSelector:
              matchLabels:
                app.kubernetes.io/name: redis
            topologyKey: kubernetes.io/hostname

replica:
  replicaCount: 2
  persistence:
    enabled: false  # 禁用持久化
  resources:
    requests:
      memory: "128Mi"
      cpu: "50m"
    limits:
      memory: "256Mi"

  # 副本也使用相同的调度配置

auth:

  app: redis-cluster
  environment: test
  team: platform

# 服务配置

  type: ClusterIP
  port: 6379
  annotations:
    service.beta.kubernetes.io/aws-load-balancer-type: "nlb"
    prometheus.io/scrape: "false"

# 网络策略配置

  enabled: false
  ingress:
